sequenceDiagram
  participant UserZ as Zcash Wallet
  participant ZC as Zcash Testnet
  participant Watcher as Relayer/Watcher
  participant Prover as Mock/Toy Prover
  participant Mina as Mina Testnet (Verifier)
  participant UI as Frontend

  UserZ->>ZC: create deposit (testnet tx or deposit intent)
  ZC-->>Watcher: notify/compact-block contains deposit
  Watcher->>Prover: build witness and produce mock proof
  Prover-->>Watcher: proof_blob
  Watcher->>Mina: submit proof_blob (Mina tx or off-chain proof submit)
  Mina-->>Watcher: txReceipt / verification result
  Mina->>UI: emit minted wrapped token event
  UI->>UserZ: show credited balance
